high_descs: Turn around and walk to the white pillar in front of you then turn right and walk to the brown chair in the left corner of the room in front of you.
Pick up the credit card that's on the chair.
Turn right and take a step then turn right and walk to the small black table with a statue on it then turn right and walk to the window then turn left to face the light.
anns.task_desc: Inspect a credit card by lamp light.

high_descs: Turn around, move forward, go in the room to the right, then had to the chair in the left corner.
Pick up the credit card on the chair.
Turn around, go back in the other room, turn right, bring the credit card over to the lamp on the floor in the far right corner.
Turn on the lamp on the floor.
anns.task_desc: Examine a credit card by the light of a tall lamp.

high_descs: Turn around and go through the entry way on your right to the end table at the end of the room, then turn left and go to the chair in the corner.
Pick up the credit card on the seat of the chair.
Turn around and walk across the room, through the entry way to another room, and across that room , then turn to your right at the wall and go to the lamp in the left corner.
Turn on the lamp in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Turn on the lamp in the corner of the office.
